asset.title: 2012, 2013, 2014 Toyota Camry 2.5L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to your 2012-2014 Toyota Camry 2.5L with this K&N air intake system. 

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=69-8620TTK

This intake system created an estimated gain of 6 horsepower at 5,605 RPM and 5 lb. ft. of torque at 4,095 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 69-8620TTK fits the following: 
2014 TOYOTA CAMRY 2.5L L4 
2013 TOYOTA CAMRY 2.5L L4 
2012 TOYOTA CAMRY 2.5L L4
